{"tid":2106031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[2006年剛創黨的公民黨] 公民黨創黨主席關信基指定位香港的政黨不宜將平反六四列入黨網","createTime":"2020-07-13T05:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:58:36.000Z","uid":78519,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"307ae7876fef561cb99c1e243a008e7c590e0807","tid":2106031,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:23:13.000Z","msg":".....//公民黨主席關信基日前發表「六四悲情或分散民主運動力量」的言論，觸發創黨後的首場風波。有公民黨創黨成員透露，過去兩日收到一些專業界別的支持者透過電郵和傳真投訴，要求公民黨解釋六四立場，更有支持者向該黨的立法會議員表示失望。關信基接受訪問解釋，他未來會繼續出席六四燭光集會，若大家再聽一次電台節目，就知道有關報道的標題不是他的原意。//.....<br />\n<br />\n.....//關信基本周日在電台解釋沒有把六四列入黨綱的原因。他說，歷史自有公論，定位香港的政黨不宜完成平反六四的歷史任務，而六四悲情或會妨礙或分散民主運動的力量。//.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20060405/UJ2OPJH7BFR4FZIMLOC4KZDBWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20060405%2FUJ2OPJH7BFR4FZIMLOC4KZDBWI%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a6298e90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20060405%2FUJ2OPJH7BFR4FZIMLOC4KZDBWI%2F&h=8c8e2a09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20060405/UJ2OPJH7BFR4FZIMLOC4KZDBWI/</a>"},{"pid":"5d0a128a510f5405ef2b6b3b2a4fe9c3b0549f8b","tid":2106031,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17b51778934cdaaf7faba17a829cfa6860943b3e","tid":2106031,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b96e91cb2e84e26fe9d54d4304adcb1ac7693a","tid":2106031,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:55:04.000Z","msg":"十一哥"},{"pid":"2ead33663d2d15bc1bdf582e390